  "title": "feat(helper): add methods to request and retrieve recommendations",
  "body": "**Summary**\r\n\r\nThis PR adds methods to algoliasearch-helper that can build a list of recommendations queries and trigger a request to the Algolia API.\r\n\r\n> [!NOTE]\r\n> A few TODO are left for subsequent PR that handle events and transforming the recommend results. In the meantime events for `change` and `result` have a `recommend:` prefix.\r\n\r\n**Result**\r\n\r\nThe helper can now interact with the Recommend API using an up-to-date search client.\r\n\r\nA test implementation (without the transformed result structure) is on CSB: https://codesandbox.io/p/sandbox/infallible-rosalind-3df2mk?file=/src/product.js.\r\n\r\nFX-2786",
